snippet.title: PAW Patrol Mighty Pups Save Adventure Bay - Announce Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Join the Mighty Pups on a super-heroic mission to Save Adventure Bay in their levelled up video game, with up to 2-players!

Coming 6th November to PlayStation. 🎮
Pre-order now 👉 www.outrightgames.com/games/paw-patrol-mighty-pups

#PAWPatrolMightyPups🐾
